  {
    question: "How does pricing work for Rogersville homes?",
    answer: "Most Rogersville homes range from $140-$325 for regular cleaning, depending on square footage, condition, and service frequency. The average 2,000-2,800 sq ft Rogersville home typically falls in the $175-$250 range for regular service. Deep cleaning costs approximately 50% more. We offer discounts for recurring weekly and bi-weekly clients. Call 256-826-1100 for your customized quote."
