  {
    question: "Do you clean homes with wood stoves and fireplaces?",
    answer: "Yes! Many Rogersville homes feature wood stoves or fireplaces for supplemental heating. We clean around these areas, handle the additional dust and ash that comes with wood burning, and maintain your hearth area. We recommend scheduling cleaning after heavy burning season for best results, though we accommodate year-round service."
